txt.en: Melethon awaits your return to the Court of Anárion where he will see you rewarded for your service!
You have been recognized as a servant to the captain of the Court of Anárion!
Quest of the Court of Anárion -- Tier 3
Service to the captain of the Court of Anárion will result in the ability to find your way through the city with less effort.
Complete quests for the benefit of the Court of Anárion!
You have performed many services for the captain of the Court of Anárion.
